 247 et seq.\n\nA. E. Gough, The Philosophy of the Upanishads; Calcutta Review, CXXXI.\n\nP. Regnaud, Materiaux pour servir a l'histoire de la Philosophic de l'Inde.\nParis, 1876.\n\nEditions of the Upanishads, their commentaries and glosses have been published\nin the Tattvabodhini patrika, and by Poley (who has also translated several\nUpanishads into French), by Roer, Cowell, Rajendralal Mitra, Hara _k_ andra\nVidyabhusha _n_ a, Vi _s_ vanatha _S_ astri, Ramamaya Tarkaratna, and others.\nFor fuller titles see Gildemeister, Bibliotheca Sanscrita, and E. Haas,\nCatalogue of Sanskrit and Pali Books in the British Museum, s. v. Upanishads.\n\n* * *\n\n[Next: I. The _Kh_ andogya-Upanishad](sbe01017.htm)\n\n"